      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"لَوْ دُعِيتُ إِلَى كُرَاعٍ لَأَجَبْتُ وَ لَوْ أُهْدِيَ إِلَيَّ كُرَاعٌ لَقَبِلْتُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4070 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (may Allah (swt) bless him and his family) said:\n\"If I were invited to a meal consisting of a trotter, I would accept, and if I were gifted a trotter, I would accept it.\""
        ]
      }
    },
